{"tid":1255332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"財委會加會37小時 陳健波望加快審議民生項目 包括人工島！！","createTime":"2019-06-24T12:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:58:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4ed68196082ee67dfde73c6369a61dd36c0936","tid":1255332,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）立法會財委會主席陳健波表示，現時財委會有至少44個項目需要審議，當中涉及769億，決定於7月加會37小時。<br />\n<br />\n陳健波指曾聯絡民主派會議召集人毛孟靜商討，但毛表示現時毋須開啟財委會會議，不過民主派會向陳提供一個項目排序。陳稱仍期望能聯同財委會副主席陳振英，與毛孟靜會面商討，仍在等候毛的回覆。<br />\n<br />\n陳指如果不加會，大量重要民生項目會被拖延4個月，例如橫洲4,000多個公營房屋單位，又提及校長加薪，要在9月前通過才能生效。因此，陳表示將在7月8日至7月20日期間，增加37小時會議，由原本12小時增至共49小時。陳強調項目全屬「民生問題」，需時間審議，不能倉促通過。<br />\n<br />\n陳又呼籲示威者保持溫和及理性，讓會議進行。他又呼籲非建制派議員放下「政治歧見」，盡快處理44個項目。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被問及具爭議的中部水域人工島項目，陳表示面對「政治現實」，如可以應先審議其餘43個項目，他亦要求政府提交新的項目排序，相信人工島會放在相當後的位置。</span></span></strong>陳有信心能在暑假完成審議「八、九成」的項目。<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳世浩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065134&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=edb14708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065134&h=731f383c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065134</a>"},{"pid":"da3e312fc0a3adda55cf271a325fa70739e489fc","tid":1255332,"uid":263161,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d34b86b9653e1ee7aa3aea0927ae30a418bc6428","tid":1255332,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"暴君還是死心不息要在香港生事。"},{"pid":"b85c4ec24b8dec20b68dbab7703ce72e8375f0a4","tid":1255332,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:57:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，加快派4000蚊進度仲好啦。<br />\n<br />\n正一垃圾"},{"pid":"445619d7ff49de5f0a67e7f70677f6e147105aa2","tid":1255332,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"政府班仆街最叻就係陰d 陰d 過 同埋 一次過打包逍過 . 唔過倒錢落海唔洗旨意有錢過民生項目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514f5db81d9b0d5fad12e071cdc44832ab0ace8f","tid":1255332,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}